 3. Build & Generate .jar File
Navigate to your project directory:
cd demo-app
mvn clean package
After a successful build, your JAR file will be in:
target/my-java-app-1.0.0.jar
To run it:
Cd demo-app/target
java -jar target/my-java-app-1.0.0.jar
java -jar demo-app-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar

